{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act27side", "eventName": "火山旅夢", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SL-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "林中小木屋", "storyInfo": "競標結束，拜松與詩懷雅慶祝他們合作演戲成功，卻很快又收到計劃被打斷的消息。錫蘭得知汐斯塔的難處，主動尋找偷挖黑曜石的工人希望提供幫助。在疑惑中，艾雅法拉見到了最後一隻仍留在汐斯塔的小黑羊。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g10_siestapremiumhotel", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_223", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_223", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二位，這是最新的民意調查結果。", "name": "市政廳職員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詩懷雅集團的“水上樂園”方案的支持率為33%，峯馳物流公司的物流中心方案支持率為21%。", "name": "市政廳職員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其餘幾位競爭者的支持率都在10%左右。", "name": "市政廳職員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖說民意調查的結果也只是影響市政廳最終決定的一部分，但就目前調查結果來看，詩懷雅集團的方案的確是佔據優勢的。", "name": "市政廳職員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用多說了，實際的形勢，相信拜松先生自己會有判斷的。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詩懷雅小姐今天特地約市政廳和我來這裡，應該不止是炫耀戰果的吧？", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#10$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。拜松先生，我想向您提出一個交易。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詩懷雅集團會退出此次競標，但相對的，我想要入股峯馳物流在這裡的公司。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這才是你最開始的目的嗎？", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#10$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不完全是，我後來又仔細想了想，你的存在對我來說並不全都是壞處。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聰明的商人總是要尋求雙贏的可能，做最符合當下利益最大化的選擇嘛。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按詩懷雅小姐的話說......如果你真的很有信心的話，就不會來找我談了。", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼對於拜松先生來說，用一定的股份認籌額度換最大的競爭對手的退出，算不算一筆好生意呢？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#3$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詩懷雅小姐的開價是？", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#12$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_stickknock", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_stickknock", "volume": 0.2, "loop": "false", "channel": "knock", "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_stickknock", "volume": 0.2, "loop": "false", "channel": "knock1", "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詩懷雅輕叩了三下桌子。"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要，這個數。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g7_siestahightechtouristzone", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_223"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_223", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二位的協議我會匯報給市長，後續進一步的安排會繼續同步給二位的。", "name": "市政廳職員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祝兩位客人在汐斯塔的行程愉快。", "name": "市政廳職員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#12$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......戲終於演完了？", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#12$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "目前為止，算是吧。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......哈哈哈......", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#4$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你笑什麼？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉抱歉......我只是沒有想到，詩懷雅局長也會用這種手段......", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#4$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要是大張旗鼓地投資峯馳物流的生意，那別說註冊自己的公司了，恐怕來汐斯塔的第一天，峯馳物流就被以一萬種理由檢舉停工了吧。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "家族的人對我有戒心，但好在並不多。只要在他們眼裡我還是那個莽撞的年輕警司，我就可以借這層外衣行事。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——我確實慶倖，沒有真的當你的競爭對手。", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這只是第一步，商業聯合會遲早會反應過來的。接下來各種各樣的刁難一定少不了。你準備好了？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經走到這一步，後悔肯定是來不及了。", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，合作愉快？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，合作愉——", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phone"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的終端？", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#12$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是，是你的吧？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#10$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phonevibration", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#10$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ringoff", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詩懷雅和拜松拿出自己的終端，兩人飛快地對視了一眼，按下了接聽鍵。"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#10$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您好，請問是“峯聯貿易”的法定代表人拜松先生嗎？", "name": "禮貌的聲音"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您好，請問是詩懷雅小姐嗎？", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "市政廳接到檢舉，貴司非法雇傭沒有身份註冊的感染者。現在請貴司立即停止一切業務。", "name": "禮貌的聲音"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請準備好以下材料，配合市政廳進行調查。首先是貴司所有感染者雇員的名單......", "name": "禮貌的聲音"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詩懷雅小姐，你的表演很有趣，確實為你爭取到了一些玩鬧的時間。但是集團對你私自做決定的行為十分不滿。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望你能意識到一點，該做的事和不該做的事都是有限度的，投資遊戲該結束了。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝您的配合，再見。", "name": "禮貌的聲音"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到此為止，希望您會好好考慮自己行為的意義。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_phonestop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#11$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是毫無理由的污衊。", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#7$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰遞交的投訴信，一目了然了啊。在合約快要簽訂的時候拖時間，他們好追上來做點其他事情。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可為什麼要用感染者做文章......汐斯塔什麼時候頒佈過為難感染者的政策？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_990_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們沒有時間對付這些無理的刁難。", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#11$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果可以說服赫爾曼市長的話——", "name": "拜松"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_990_1#11$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1033_swire2_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說得沒錯，突破口的確在赫爾曼本人身上。可他有什麼理由，一定站在我們這邊......", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，如果我沒猜錯的話，他現在也面臨著別的壓力吧。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_1033_swire2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫爾曼市長，見您一面很不容易。", "name": "哥倫比亞代表"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_544_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_544_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為之前我給出的回覆已經很明確，我們之間沒有必須要當面會談的問題。", "name": "赫爾曼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_544_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_544_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，哥倫比亞尊重汐斯塔作為獨立城邦的一切權利。我今天來到這裡，是為了和您談另一件事——汐斯塔的感染者問題。", "name": "哥倫比亞代表"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_544_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "赫爾曼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_544_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_544_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照哥倫比亞聯邦法律，感染者必須繳納足夠的醫療保險才有權利在移動城市生活。否則就要加入拓荒隊了。", "name": "哥倫比亞代表"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前汐斯塔不是移動城市，所以沒有受到這條法律的約束。但是從現在開始，我們有必要重新探討一下法治的意義。", "name": "哥倫比亞代表"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_544_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的文字遊戲，就是你們的施壓方式？", "name": "赫爾曼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_544_1#6$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_544_1#6$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望您認清現狀，赫爾曼市長。", "name": "哥倫比亞代表"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們現在並不是處在協商的立場上。", "name": "哥倫比亞代表"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g3_siestanewstreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從什麼時候開始買個黑曜石都要這麼偷偷摸摸的了？", "name": "疲憊的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4106_bryota_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒辦法啊，最近查得嚴，但機會都是留給你們這種消息靈通、懂得把握機會的人的！", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "物流中心很快就要建成了，不少商人等著收購黑曜石呢。", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，汐斯塔的黑曜石，現在還是什麼稀罕的東西嗎？你自己店裡也偷偷藏了不少吧，何必來找我。", "name": "委頓的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4106_bryota_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們想要的是最近才開採出來的，說什麼......這種受到火山熱能影響的黑曜石，蘊含著大地的能量，有非常神奇的保健功效！", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "疲憊的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4106_bryota_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，不逗你們了。除了這筐黑曜石，還有沒有最近挖出來的？如果你們還有的話，我有個管道，品相好的話，有買家出這個數。", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#17$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃尼斯用手比劃了一個數字。"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個價？那有的，就在前幾天我還去挖了不少呢。", "name": "精神的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4106_bryota_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？就在最近挖的嗎？", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#20$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯嗯，我還留了幾個極漂亮的——你看，這幾塊的品相是不是很讚？", "name": "精神的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不錯。", "name": "錫蘭"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1003_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1003_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼可以請你再跟我講一些，你們違法私採黑曜石的事嗎？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1003_1#8$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃尼斯！你騙我！你什麼時候學壞的？", "name": "慌張的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4106_bryota_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，這也不算騙吧，是一位嗓門很大的警察教我的......抱歉啦，傑克大叔，這也是為了你好呀，別拿自己的健康開玩笑啊。", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#17$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是向你打聽一點事情，還請你配合我們的調查啦。", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#17$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g9_purewhitevolcano_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們說完了，要交代的就是這些了......", "name": "灰心喪氣的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會被關起來嗎......？", "name": "無精打采的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1003_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你們現在挖回來的黑曜石準備賣給誰？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1003_1#11$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4106_bryota_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是佩利佩嗎？", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#17$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不......佩利佩很早之前就不再從我們這裡收購黑曜石了，而且真的是說到做到，一顆都不要。我們拿去再好的，他一眼都不看。", "name": "灰心喪氣的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗐，現在你們讓我說這些有什麼用？", "name": "無精打采的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫爾曼想一出是一出，先是不讓挖黑曜石，又說火山要爆發了，結果我們搬到這裡快兩年了，也沒見火山冒出一縷煙。", "name": "無精打采的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不看看早幾年靠什麼賺錢......", "name": "灰心喪氣的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1003_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，汐斯塔的感染者政策不是很寬鬆嗎......？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1003_1#11$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們還是沒有工作了啊，礦場那麼多待業工人要是都去做司機，汐斯塔能直接被拉著再跑幾公里。", "name": "灰心喪氣的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況我已經感染了，還能做什麼呢？峯馳物流一來，又多少人沒了工作，市長還要拆商業街。拆了要幹什麼？把我們都趕走嗎？", "name": "無精打采的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4106_bryota_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能，可能市長會頒佈什麼政策幫助你們的......", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#14$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想什麼呢，你沒聽到消息嗎？我們這些感染了的就要被趕走了，連哥倫比亞人都來了。", "name": "無精打采的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1003_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們從哪裡聽到的？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1003_1#11$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們可是知道哥倫比亞怎麼對感染者的，要真有什麼事，我們自己先去荒野上拓荒好了。", "name": "無精打采的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫爾曼個貝殼腦袋......真的是個貝殼腦袋！", "name": "灰心喪氣的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4106_bryota_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃呃......咳！咳！", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#10$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼了？生病了嗎？", "name": "灰心喪氣的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4106_bryota_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒沒，呃，我......", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#17$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1003_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1003_1#7$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4106_bryota_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，錫蘭醫生，他們也是......", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#10$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "市長先生肯定也很辛苦，你也不要太生氣......", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#10$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1003_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是的，我沒有在為這件事生氣。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1003_1#7$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本來以為只是警告幾個偷採的工人別再去了，但是哥倫比亞人來了，事情就不一樣了......", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1003_1#7$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是汐斯塔自己的問題。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1003_1#7$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1003_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1003_1#6$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1003_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大叔，就你們知道的，現在還有多少人在挖黑曜石？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1003_1#6$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "無精打采的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "灰心喪氣的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1003_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者我直說吧，我並不是要送你們去見警察。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1003_1#6$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃尼斯剛剛也說了，我是一名醫生，我知道單純地阻止你們去挖黑曜石是不現實的，我只是想幫你們解決這個問題......請相信我。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1003_1#6$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，現在能不能告訴我？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1003_1#6$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼意思，你要幫我們？", "name": "無精打采的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，你是......？而且，為什麼？", "name": "無精打采的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下，這位小姐，你有點眼熟......", "name": "灰心喪氣的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4106_bryota_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼，你總算發現了！黑曜石音樂節的轉播總看過吧，好幾次和赫爾曼市長一同出席閉幕式的那位小姐總有印象吧。", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......誰？不不不，我是說我曾經見過一位和你長得很像的女士......", "name": "灰心喪氣的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是很久以前的事了，我們都還在黑曜石礦場工作。", "name": "灰心喪氣的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時候有一個從維多利亞來的學者。明明還懷著身孕，但每天都往礦場跑，說要調查什麼生態環境。", "name": "灰心喪氣的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然她對礦上的東西瞭解得不算多，但她確實對我們挺好的......", "name": "灰心喪氣的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，我想起來了，她的名字好像是叫......芭樂......不對，芭芭拉。", "name": "灰心喪氣的工人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1003_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1003_1#5$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g5_siestaunbuiltland_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$beach", "channel": "beach", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "背著礦燈的生物走走停停，遙望著老汐斯塔海灘的方向。"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伯德坐在沙灘上，信手撥著琴弦。"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wdnguitarpizz", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#8$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您平時都待在這裡嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，這裡還能看到老汐斯塔呢......", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟音樂是很好聽的，海浪聲透過風傳過來，很配吉他聲。", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#8$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我沒想到你會問這個問題......原來你也是一個願意搭話的人呀。", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？這不是很正常的舉動嗎......？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......也對，是我有些狹隘了吧。", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果萬物都能對話，或許樂聲就是最好的語言。即使語言不通，也可以傳遞你真實的思想——真不錯，感覺是某種新的靈感。", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wdnguitarstrum", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伯德彈起一首舒緩的小曲，海浪起起伏伏，正和著她的節拍。"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們是這首曲子最早的聽眾。", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“你們”？啊......您是指這些羽獸和小草嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？不是啊。", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡不是還有一個聽眾嗎？", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#8$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "beach", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伯德指向按理來說空無一物的臺階。"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1013_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1013_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "背著礦燈的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1013_1#1$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛才不是一直在和它說話嗎？", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伯德小姐......您也能看到它？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#5$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "背著礦燈的生物站在沙灘上，呆呆地看著遠處那一線老汐斯塔的影子。它試圖踏入海水，但幾次躊躇，最終又走回了地塊上。"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sheeprun", "loop": "true", "channel": "step1", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "step1", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它的蹄子有節奏地踏著地面，彷彿在配合著音樂的拍子，但又好像不是，只是堅持著一個它自己的節奏。"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咚咚、咚咚、咚咚......"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，從來到汐斯塔的那一天起，我一直都能看到。", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有？還有很多這種生物嗎？", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#4$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......很可惜，我只能看到這一個。", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伯德看著眼前這個生物背上的礦燈，頭上的礦帽和護目鏡。"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大概是我之前在老汐斯塔的時候，給那些礦工們寫過一首曲子，而它恰巧很喜歡和礦石有關的東西？", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我再給它彈一遍那首曲子吧。", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#2$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#2$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wdnguitarpizz", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伯德重新撥動琴弦，阿黛爾收好裙擺，坐在伯德的身旁。"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣一想，或許我寫過的曲子還找不出一首可以代表我人生的，但是可能也有那麼一兩首能成為別人的慰藉......", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......雖然聽眾只是一隻，小黑羊？", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但也不錯！", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#8$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......原來它留下來是為了聽您彈琴啊。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說你還能看到其他的小黑羊，它們都在哪裡？", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們......它們突然都不見了，我也不知道它們都去了哪裡。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那它們也會和它一樣吃路牌嗎？", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "似乎沒有......", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，那我有了一個想法。", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得它吃這些路牌，會不會是因為，它迷路了？", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1013_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "背著礦燈的生物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1013_1#1$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}